text: Paul O'Brien (born 16 July 1968) is a New Zealand equestrian. He competed in the team eventing at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of New Zealand Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Auckland
